Class PaginationDto

java.lang.Object
de.dedede.model.data.dtos.PaginationDto
All Implemented Interfaces:

public class PaginationDto extends Object implements Serializable
This DTO (data transfer object) is responsible for aggregating and encapsulating data about the pagination of the page for transfer.
